---
title: Fiery Gochujang Pork Udon with baby corn and coriander
description: These pork noodles are spicy, fragrant and delicious. The sauce contains hints of lemongrass and ginger, while the coriander topping adds a freshness and herbiness that's pleasing to the palette.
